Task: What is the numeric equivalent of -r-xrw-r--?
To find the numeric value, we break the string into groups of three (ignoring the first dash which signifies the file type):
Owner (r-x): 4 (read) + 0 + 1 (execute) = 5
Group (rw-): 4 (read) + 2 (write) + 0 = 6
Others (r--): 4 (read) + 0 + 0 = 4
Result: 564

